content:
I've a warning about a missing example for a data type profile.
I thought it was enough to have an example compliant with a profile that uses that data type profile (and implementing that data type)
what I should check ?
If the data type profile is in your build, is it being built correctly?
If you're confident your profile is being enforced in the example, you can suppress the message. The validator warns about the lack of an explicit listed example.
Giorgio Cangioli has marked this topic as resolved.
